Package: simplemarkdown
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Lightweight Markdown editor with live preview
 SimpleMarkdown is a cross-platform Markdown editor featuring a custom
 text engine built on PieceTable, real-time GFM preview powered by
 cmark-gfm, and synchronized scrolling between editor and preview panes.
